{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L742","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"viewForAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view that requested the annotation view.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to display an annotation image instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method or have it return ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for that annotation, then implement","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instead.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"annotation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is an instance of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" (or equal to the map view’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property), return an instance of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(or a subclass thereof).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" to use for a given ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" object on your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map.","type":"text"}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"require the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"individual annotations."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"View representing an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference"},{"text":" on screen.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNUserLocation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference"},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"}}}